Faisal Baig is a Wakhi tribesman who becomes Mortenson’s bodyguard. Baig guides George                 McCown on a climbing trip, during which he meets Mortenson. Over time Baig takes on                 personal responsibility for Mortenson’s safety in Pakistan. The CAI carries out                 several projects in Baig’s home village, and Mortenson and McCown are visiting there                 when Baig brings them news of the 9/11 terrorist attack.